inn1.comm: full and wide of off and McCullum watches it go by
McCullum walks down the tack, McKay bends his back and hurries him up as he defends into the off side
full on middle and McCullum drives to mid on who is quite close to the bowlers' stumps
back of a length and it's been a great start from McKay who is asking a few questions. He pushes McCullum back and he defends into the leg side
good channel again from McKay and McCullum moves back and defends with soft hands into the leg side and they take a quick single to get underway
McKay finishes with a cracking delivery in the channel, Guptill decides early to leave the ball and it jags back towards off stump and bounces just wide and over the top of off stump
back of a length, good start from Bollinger, and McCullum moves back and across and plays to backward point
McCullum advances and Bollinger tries to adjust by going wider of off but he gets it wrong and it flies through the cordon to third man for a couple
good length on middle and McCullum moves back and defends back along the pitch
around the wicket this time and a good length ball forces him back again and he pushes back to the bowler
Bollinger loses his line and bowls well down leg and the angle from around the wicket is too much for Haddin and he can't get to it
even heavier from Bollinger and McCullum is back and across and defending forward of point
angled into leg stump from around the wicket and McCullum misses out as it takes him high on the pad
good length but a fraction straight and McCullum clips it off his hip to short fine leg
full in length but quite straight and Guptill drives but gets an inside edge back onto his pad and into the leg side
better channel this time and Guptill defends with hard hands to cover point
McKay oversteps and he strays in line, it takes Guptill on the thigh and runs fine for four. Free-hit coming up
Guptill sits back in the crease and waits for the slower ball out the back of the hand and launches it over mid wicket and into the stands for six
good length and it seams back into the pads, Guptill misses and the Australian's go up but Umpire Rauf says not out and it looked to be sliding down leg just enough
back into his channel and Guptill defends off the outside edge to third man
back of a length in at middle and McCullum is beaten as he tries to play through the leg side, McKay leads the appeal but it's a fraction high
back of a length outside off and Guptill plays inside the line
fullish in length this time and Guptill defends nicely to point
fullish in length and wide of off stump and Guptill allows it through to Haddin
a fraction fuller and wide of off stump and Guptill is happy to let it go by
good channel wide of off and Guptill shoulders' arms
a touch shorter in length but hits a great channel and Guptill is content on leaving it alone
good length as McCullum comes down the track, he is hurried up and he pushes in the air to Ponting at mid off
good length but angled into the body and Taylor whips it off his hip to fine leg for a couple
full in length and beaten outside off, well bowled
good fullish length and angled into middle and leg and worked to fine leg
back of a length in at the body and he beats Guptill's bat and it takes him on the body and they take a leg bye into the off side

Taylor moves back, defends into the leg side, both batsmen hesitate before continuing the run and a good throw from mid wicket hits and Guptill is just short of his ground. Australia are very sharp today!
back of a length and Taylor plays it well, dropping his hands underneath the bounce
good channel again wide of off and Taylor allows it go through to Haddin
back of a length on middle and leg and Taylor defends into the on side
good length but well wide of off and Taylor shoulders arms
top of off stump and Taylor pushes into the covers
fullish outside off and Taylor pushes into the off side
back of a length and Stewart defends into the leg side
back of a length and he tries to play into the leg side but is taken high on the pad
good length, a fraction too straight, and Stewart moves across his stumps and defends off the inside edge to fine leg for four
great channel asking plenty of questions and Stewart defends back along the pitch
shorter in length and defended into the leg side
angled into the body and he works it behind square on the leg side for a couple
full on off stump and Taylor drives to mid off where Ponting dives to collect
cracking delivery from Johnson has Taylor playing outside off and it just beats the outside edge
good length again on middle and Taylor defends off the outside edge to point
cracking bumper and Taylor ducks underneath
back of a length and Taylor pushes into the off side for a quick single to Ponting at mid off
full outside off and Stewart plays with no conviction and edges through to Haddin, New Zealand in early trouble here at the 'Cake Tin'
fullish on off stump and Taylor defends into the off side
full delivery and Taylor comes forward and pushes into the off side
good length and Taylor comes forward and defends off the inside edge onto his pad
fullish in length again and Taylor pushes into the off side
good length but a fraction straight and he works it off his hip behind square on the leg side for a couple
shortish and it's just wide enough for Taylor to cut backward of point for four
full and wide of off stump and Styris allows it through to the keeper
back of a length and Styris guides to third man
good length, a fraction wide and Taylor mistimes the cut to point
half volley wide of off stump and Taylor hammers it through the covers for four, great timing
good length on off stump and Taylor moves back and defends back into the off side
an absolute cracking delivery from Johnson beats Taylor outside off
back of a length wide of off and allowed through to the keeper
fuller and into off stump and Styris drives to mid off
good length and Styris moves back and defends into the off side
fullish in length draws Styris forward and he defends into the off side
back of a length and into the pads and Styris misses out as it takes him on the thigh pad
good length into the body and Styris pushes off the back foot to mid on
full in length and Taylor drives powerfully on the up to cover
full and well wide of off stump and called wide by umpire Baxter
full and wide of off stump and Taylor drives but misses
full outside off stump and Taylor drives but straight into the covers
full and very wide of off and Taylor loses his poise and drives to the cover sweeper
fullish in length wide of off stump and Styris square drives backward of point, third man collects and they get just the single
good length but down leg and Haddin is close to it but it keeps low and goes under his gloves for four, plus the wide
half volley on off and Taylor crunches it to Hussey at cover
Bollinger over steps and Styris punches through cover on the up for three
length ball and Taylor swings hard but misses as he tries to heave through the leg side
good length and Taylor defends to cover
nice channel again from Bollinger and Taylor pushes to cover point
good length on off stump and Taylor plays into the off side
back of a length and Taylor drives on the up to the man on the fence at point
good length and Styris plays into the off side
back of a length and defended into the off side off the back foot
shorter this time and Taylor hops back and defends with soft hands into the off side
slower ball bouncer and it's down the leg side
short and wide and Taylor cuts over point for four, super stroke
good length anfd Taylor pushes nicely back down the pitch
yorker length outside off and he drives into the off side
good length in at the body and Taylor fends off his body into the leg side
short and just enough width to cut to third man
good length just wide of off stump and Styris uses the pace and plays to point
slower ball and Styris pushes into the off side but can't get the single
back of a length and punched into the off side to the sweeper
full outside off and driven through the off side field to the man on the fence
good length but a fraction too straight and Styris plays into the leg side for an easy single
full and wide and Styris drives, it sounds like an edge but nobody on the field thinks so and it's just a dot ball
fullish and played to cover
short and pulled out to deep square leg
back of a length and Taylor plays square of the wicket to point
slower ball and Taylor comes forward and plays to deep point
fullish in length and square driven to third man. Lets have a drink
full outside off and Styris drives to deep point for a couple
tossed up and worked through square leg to the sweeper
nicely flighted and Taylor drives neatly to long on
full and wide and Stryis drives, using the pace and Johnson is beaten by the spin at backward point and the misfield allows for four
full and driven square on the off side to the sweeper
back of a length and cut/guided to short third man
full in length and Taylor drives to mid off
bumper from Watson and Taylor ducks underneath
good length outside off and Taylor square drives off the inside edge into the on side for a single
full on middle and clipped through the leg side to the sweeper for a single
pitched up and driven to mid on for a quick single, well run
slower ball out the back of the hand and Styris defends back along the pitch
well flighted outside off and driven to the off side sweeper
full in length and defended off the inside edge back along the pitch
full outside off and mistimed drive into the off side
tossed up and driven to long on
back of a length and Taylor leaves it alone outside off
good length but too straight and Taylor whips it to mid wicket for a single

bumper from Watson outside off and Talylor pulls it high into the leg side and Bollinger moves around from fine leg to take an easy catch in the deep. Watson, once again, makes the important breakthrough
full on off stump and Styris drives to mid on
good length and Styris moves back and plays into the off side
back of a length and Vettori cuts off the bottom edge back past his stumps
good length and he moves back and punches through the off side to the sweeper
good channel and Vettori pushes firmly to mid off
tossed up outside off and Styris uses the spin to play to deep square leg
angled into middle from around the wicket and defended with soft hands into the off side
full on off stump and Vettori sweeps to deep backward square
full in length outside off and Styris goes down on one knee and paddle sweeps to fine leg for a couple
tossed up on off stump and and swept fine to Watson at fine leg
full again and driven towards mid on but mid wicket moves quickly to save the single
half volley outside off and driven to cover
half volley on off stump and driven strongly to mid off
bouncer from Watson and Styris sways inside the line
back of a length on off and Styris moves back and defends to backward point for a quick single
good channel and Vettori pushes off the inside half of the bat to mid wicket
good length, Vettori comes forward and pushes with soft hands into the off side and they take a quick single
nicely flighted and Vettori charges and has to defend back along the pitch to the bowler, well bowled
tossed up outside off and Vettori tries to sweep it, it gets the toe and falls safely into the off side
angled into leg and flicked into the leg side for a single
too straight and worked into the leg side
flighted well down leg and Vettori sweeps from the middle of the bat to long leg for four well needed runs
straighter on the stumps and Vettori still sweeps into the leg side
good bumper from Watson, hurries Vettori up but he pulls nicely for four through backward square leg, good stroke in the end
good length and punched to point off the back foot
back of a length but more width this time and Vettori cuts to the man in the deep at point
full and angled down leg and Styris clips it nicely to Bollinger at fine leg and they have enough time for two
back of a length on off and Stryris works it to mid wicket for a single
short and wide and Vettori misses out by cutting off the bottom of the bat straight into the ground on the off side
full outside off and driven on the up through the covers to the sweeper
full and a hint of late inswing as Vettori clips it off middle through square leg to the sweeper
full on leg stick and he clips it nicely but straight to square leg
half volley wide of off and driven sweetly through the off side to the sweeper
good length on middle and leg and Vettori pushes to mid wicket
Vettori walks across his stumps and whips the low full toss through the leg side to the sweeper at square leg
around the wicket and angled down the leg side
full outside off and driven to mid off
full again and driven firmly to mid off
back of a length and pulled through mid wicket to the sweeper
full length and driven powerfully to mid on
full outside off and Styris tries to break the field up by going over mid on, he mistimes it and it bounces just in front of Hauritz at mid on
back of a length and worked to mid wicket
full and wide and square driven nicely but straight to backward point
angled into the body and Styris fends off his hip into the leg side
bouncer is very short and Vettori goes underneath and it's called wide
walks across his stumps and angled into the pads and he clips it to fine leg
good length but too straight and worked to fine leg
Johnson tries around the wicket and it doesn't work immediately as he bowls down leg
Vettori walks across his stumps again and Johnson follows him and Vettori plays with sift hands into the off side
full on leg stump and flicked off his pads to fine leg
full and Vettori drives with a cross bat to mid off and takes the single
half volley on middle and Styris clubs it over straight mid on for four, good gutsy stroke
back of a length and played with soft hands backward of point for a single
fuller and Vettori plays it through mid on to the man on the fence
shorter from Hopes and Styris pulls his through square leg to the sweeper
back of a length and Vettori drags it off the inside half of the bat through forward square leg to the sweeper
slightly short and Vettori moves back and plays to fine leg
back of a length and Styris goes back and cuts, using the pace, fine of short third man for a couple
nicely flighted and Stryis goes across his stumps and plays to mid wicket for a single
short and Vettori has ample time to move back and whip it to fine leg
tossed up wide of off stump and he pushes into the off side for an easy single
well flighted on middle and Vettori sweeps to fine leg
good length and played into the leg side for a comfortable single
good length and Styris is back and playing to the leg side
short and pulled into the leg swide to the man on the fence at mid wicket
good length but Styris plays it well and guides to third man off the full face
back of a length and played off the insie edge to mid wicket
back of a length and Vettori swats it back to the bowler
tossed up outside off from around the wicket and he's beaten outside off
beaten outside off again as he tries to use the pace and play into the off side
full and driven to long off for a couple, well gapped
tossed up and hammered over mid wicket for six, that's massive and that's his fifty
full and driven to long off but Styris decides not to run so that he can take full toll of the free-hit
tossed up and Styris can't get hold of it, edging into the leg side
played to deep square leg for a single
short and wide and cut to point
good length ball and it seams back into him, he gets an inside edge and hits middle and off stump, great delivery
angled into the pads and he misses out
full and driven off the middle of the bat to point
played with soft hands into the off side and takes off for a quick single
back of a length and played into the off side
good channel in at the body and Hopkins plays back to the bowler
back of a length outside off and cut to deep point
short and wide and Vettori tries to cut but misses
Vettori steps away to leg, Bollinger hits the perfect channel, Vettori plays and misses and Bollinger cleans him out, well bowled buyt some poor batting from New Zealand here
back of a length and played to backward point
slower ball wide of off stump and it keeps low and Hopkins plays and misses
bumper and Hopkins pulls but it takes him on the forearm and goes high into the air, Haddin collects and appeals but it's given not out
back of a length and played into the off side
full and driven through the off side to the sweeper
back of a length and worked off his hip for a single to square leg
good length and played to point
back of a length and McCullum is beaten outside off
back of a length and McCullum defends into the on side for a quick single
back of a length and Hopkins pushes with soft hands into the off side for a well judged single
good length and McCullum drives firmly to cover
back of a length and McCullum drives off the outside edge to third man
good channel, Hopkins moves forward and pushes into the gap at point to the man in the deep
full and wide and square driven through backward point for a couple to third man
half volley and driven sweetly through the covers for four, super shot from the wee man
better length and defended into the off side
full and driven through cover pont to the man in the deep
good length just on off stump and played with soft hands to backward point
great channel but McCullum uses soft hands to good effect and guides to third man
bumper and McCullum gets a top edge onto his helmet, high into the air behind square on the leg side, but it falls safely and they get a single
good channel and defended to cover
Hopkins uses his feet and Bollinger bowls full and Hopkins lofts it back past the bowler for four, great stroke
cracking delivery from Bollinger beats Hopkins for pace and flicks his back leg on the way through, Haddin appeals but it's not out
back of a length and Hopkins drives on the up but off the bottom edge and back to the bowler
full on middle and driven through the on side past Johnson at mid on for three
pitched up and driven through the off side field to the man on the fence at cover point
fuller again and McCullum plays halfa drive and is beaten
full length outside off and played nicely to third man
bumper from Watson, Hopkins goes back and shapes to pull but then decides against it
drags the slower ball down short and Hopkins cuts over backward point for four, great shot
back of a length in at the body and Hopkins works through the leg side for a couple, well run and well gapped
tossed up and played to short third man, looks for the single but can't get it
well flighted and it turns sharply and he plays into the leg side
tossed up and driven off the outside edge to short third man
Hopkins looks to comes down the pitch but it's short and he moves but to cut but edges it to Haddin and Australia are jubilant again
short and punched through the off side to the sweeper at point
tossed up and defended into the off side
full on middle and Tuffey's weight is back and he whips it to Ponting on the bounce
full and played to mid wicket with more assurity this time
better length on middle stump and played to mid wicket
back of a length pushed into the off side
bumper from Watson, Tuffey tries to pull but misses and it's through to Haddin
angled down leg, he gets an inside edge onto the pad, looks for the single but can't get one
good channel outside off and beaten outside off
full outside off and McCullum drives off the outside edge to third man
low full toss and Tuffey drives through the covers to the off side sweeper for a couple
full outside off and Tuffey looks to drive but misses
good length and played into the leg side for a quick single
walks across to the off side and it goes over middle and leg stump
bouncer from Watson, Tuffey pulls but misses
decent length and Tuffey leans back and pulls over mid wicket for a couple to the sweeper
good length and played into the leg side for an easy single
full and driven back to the bowler and Watson throws back at the stumps but it's well wide
good length and driven on the up off the outside edge to third man
angled into the pads, Tuffey misses out as it takes him on the thigh pad and they take a leg bye
fullish in length, draws Tuffey into the drive but he's beaten
back of a length, Tuffey moves back and defends into the off side
good length again and Tuffey is back and defending into the covers for a single
good length and beaten outside off, McCullum is annoyed at himself for playing at it
full and wide down leg
back of a length McCullum plays off the outside half of the bat to third man where Hauritz misfields and they get a second
pitched up and played through the leg side for one to the sweeper at backward square
full and punched back down the ground through mid on to the man on the rope
fullish length and Tuffey drives on the up through extra cover for four, super timing
slower ball bouncer and he pulls off the edge into the ground to short fine leg for a single
back of a length into the body and he gets it on the body and they take a quick single into the off side
full and driven in the air but bounces well short of the man at long off
McCullum advances and hits over extra cover for four, great stroke
fullish in length and Tuffey plays and misses outside off
full in length, hint of away swing to the right hander and he plays and misses
back of a length and he pushes into the on side
half volley wide of off stump and Tuffey guides to third man
good length and McCullum tries to play through the leg side, he gets a leading edge straight up into the air and Johnson moves back and collects the catch
back of a length and Tuffey pushes through mid on for an easy single past the bowler
full and driven through extra cover for a couple to the man at long off
shortish delivery and Tuffey pulls through forward square leg
bouncer and Bond ducks underneath as it goes over middle stump
another bouncer and Bond ducks underneath again
cracking short ball and Bond plays it awkwardly and it takes him on the forearm and falls into the leg side
another bumper from McKay and Bond goes underneath again
short and fast from Johnson, Tuffey pulls but misses
yorker and Tuffey digs it out into the off side for a quick single
back of a length and played to mid wicket
full and well wide of off stump and Bond swings but misses andis disappointed it's not called wide
great bouncer from Johnson and Bond goes underneath again
full and just outside the line of off stump, Bond drives and misses
slower ball out the back of the hand and Tuffey pulls over mid wicket for six, superb striking
full and driven wide of long off for a couple
yorker wide of off stump and Tuffey plays and misses
half volley and leg stump and Tuffey drives neatly through mid on to the man on the rope. Looking like a batsman these days is Tuffey
short ball and Bond tries to pull, it glaces his helmet and goes through to Haddin on the bounce
another bouncer, Bond lifts his head and tries to heave it through mid wicket but misses
fullish in length and outside off and Tuffey plays and misses
full on middle and Tuffey drives off the inside edge to mid wicket
full length and Bond heaves it through square leg to the sweeper
well directed yorker and Tuffey tries to drive hard through the off side, he gets a bottom edge an they take an easy single
half volley on off and Bond leans back and crunches it through mid off for a couple to the man on the fence
another good yorker but Bond swings hard and drives to long off for a couple as he didn't time it well enough
good yorker and Tuffey swings it down to long off for a single
low full toss and Bond swings it off the inside edge through square leg for one
yorker and Tuffey digs it out back to the bowler
full but Tuffey leans back and swings it over backward point for a couple to third man
half volley and Tuffey sits back in his crease and swings it over extra cover for two
low full toss which Tuffey hits high into the air and Ponting moves forward from the mid wicket boundary, gets under it safely and completes the catch

inn2.comm: fullish in the channel and Watson allows it through to the keeper
back of a length and Watson moves back and guides to third man
good length and Haddin is back and defending into the off side
back of a length and played nicely into the off side towards point
Bond bends his back and Haddin is back and defending nicely into the off side
good channel again from Bond and Haddin plays firmly into the off side field
back of a length and Watson allows it through to the keeper
good channel and it nips back and it's left alone
good length again and Watson is happy to let it go by the off stump
Tuffey bends his back and hits the deck harder forcing Watson to play into the off side
Tuffey hits a good channel again and it seams back into him, he tries to guide it to third man, gets an inside edge past his leg stump and away for four through fine leg
good length and wider of off, he cuts but straight into the ground to Nathan McCullum at point
fuller length and Haddin drives on the up through the covers for three, Vettori does well in the deep to prevent the boundary
good channel wide of off and left alone by Watson
fuller in length and Watson drives nicely but straight to Guptill at cover
shorter this time and Watson is onto it in a flash and pulling to Southee on the fence at square leg
cracking channel and Haddin is beaten outside off
genuine half volley and Haddin punches back down the ground for four, great timing, played with such ease
good channel and Watson guides neatly to third man
slightly shorter and Haddin pulls off the bottom edge into his pad
full on middle and Haddin drives sweetly to Brendon McCullum at mid on
good length outside off and Haddin plays to Nathan McCullum at point
slower ball on a good length but Haddin just hits through the line beautifully and over the bowler for four, great shot
full on middle and crunched to mid on
back of a length and Watson uses the pace to guide to third man
back of a length and Haddin plays late and pushes to point
good bouncer and Haddin ducks underneath
back of a length and cut to third man
back of a length and wide which allows Watson to cut backward of point to third man for a couple
good channel and Watson defends into the off side
full and driven back hard at the bowler
fullish in length and Haddin drives on the up through mid off for four, super stroke
back of a length and wide enough to cut to third man
good channel and Watson plays with soft hands into the off side
good length and seams back into Watson but Tuffey can't beat his solid defence
good channel and Watson guides to Styris at gully
half volley and cracked back at Bond who does well to stop it
perfect length from Bond, top of off and Haddin defends into the off side
Bond bounces him out, a good quick bouncer tkes Haddin high on the bat as he pulls and it loops to Southee at square leg

good quick bumper to Ponting first up and he is surprised by the pace, shapes to pull but then decides against it, it takes him on the helmet, close to his gloves and it goes through to Hopkins, New Zealand go up and ask the question and umpire Baxter raises the finger
back of a length in the channel and White allows it through to the keeper
back of a length and White is back and defending into the off side
angled down the leg side and called wide
tossed up and into leg stump, Watson drives to long on for a couple
tossed up, drifts into leg and played to square leg inside the 30m ring
back of a length and punched back to the bowler
flat and punched towards mid on but Vettori fields well
arm ball from Vettori hurries Watson up and he gets an inside edge into the leg side
flatter and drifts into leg stump and it takes him on the pads and falls into the leg side
back of a length, Watson cuts but misses
short and Watson pulls through mid wicket for four, great strike
another short delivery and Watson is hurried on the pull and it spoons to mid on but bounces just in front
slower ball in the channel and Watson lets it go
back of a length in the channel and Watson moves back and plays into the off side
good channel and Watson guides to third man
well flighted and Watson is forward and defending to the off side
tossed up on off and Watson comes forward and defends into the leg side for a quick single
arm ball drifts into White and beats the bat, takes him on the pad but it's going down leg
much slower this time and White plays into the off side
well flighted and fuller and White drives stongly into the off side
tossed up and White plays into the off side
in the channel back of a length and guided to third man
back of a length in at off stump and White plays into the off side
bends his back again and forces White back into a strong defensive stroke
good channel again and White is back and playing into the off side and looking for one but it's not there
great channel again and defended strongly to point
good delivery to finish and White punches to point
nicely flighted and Watson is forward and defending into the pitch
tossed up again and Watson pushes into mid wicket for a single
pitched up and White plays a little early and drives back to Vettori in the air for a time but it bounces well in front of him
full in length and driven back past the bowler to long off
arm ball from Vettori and Watson moves back and punches to long on
full and wide and White square drives to deep point
full and wide and White drives to mid off with some power
back of a length and White is back and playing off the inside edge to square leg
Southee goes fuller this time and White hits nicely through the line and over the bowlers head and it bounces just in front of the rope for four
back of a length and Southee really bends his back this time and he beats the outside edge
fuller in length and White drives sweetly to mid off

good length ball and White tries to hit over the top again but closes the face slightly and it goes high in the air and Vettori moves back from mid off to take the catch, important breakthrough from the hosts
tossed up and Voges drives to mid on
fuller again and Voges defends into the off side
angled into leg and he plays to mid wicket
well flighted and Voges is forward and defending back along the pitch
tossed up and driven firmly back at Vettori
Vettori drags this down and Voges punches to cover
back of a length but too straight and Watson punches through mid wicket for a couple
good channel outside off and Watson allows it through to the keeper
back of a length and Watson defends back to the bowler
Southee continues to bend his back and Watson punches to point
good length and Watson drives on the up and McCullum dives forward at cover to collect on the bounce
good length Watson plays into the leg side for a single
good channel and Watson plays with soft hands into the off side for a single
back of a length and Voges pushes into the on side for a single
full from Tuffey and Watson drives in the air past the bowler and down the ground for four
back of a length and Watson plays with an open face to backward point

back of a length and Watson uses the width to play to third man
fuller from Southee and Watson plays into the off side with soft hands
back of a length and Watson is back quickly and pulling through the gap between mid on and mid wicket for four, great shot
short and wide and cracked to point
good length and Voges plays off the back foot into the on side
back of a length and Voges comes forward and defends into the off side
a fraction short and Voges pulls through mid wicket to the man on the fence. It's time for a drink
good length but angled down leg and Voges works it off his hip to deep square leg
good length on off stump and defended back along the pitch
back of a length and Watson plays with soft hands into the off side
strays down leg and Watson clips it to deep square leg
good length but too straight and Voges plays off his hip into the leg side
fuller this time on middle stump and Watson drives to long on
tossed up and driven to long off
well flighted but slightly wide of off and driven to cover
flat in at off and driven in the air to cover but it bounces just short of the man
tossed up and driven to long on
straighter this time and played to square leg
full and straight and Watson waits for it and drives back past the bowler to long on
